and Financial Conference
pose on the hotel log.

00:13:48.495 --> 00:13:50.230 align:middle line:84%
These meetings are
designed to promote trade

00:13:50.230 --> 00:13:51.398 align:middle line:90%
in the post-war world,

00:13:51.398 --> 00:13:52.565 align:middle line:84%
and to create a foundation
for a lasting peace.

00:13:52.565 --> 00:14:01.641 align:middle line:90%
