00:31:59.685 --> 00:32:00.953 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: OK.

00:32:00.953 --> 00:32:03.389 align:middle line:84%
>> KH: So there's the US,
Britain, France, Germany,

00:32:03.389 --> 00:32:07.292 align:middle line:90%
China, Saudi Arabia, Japan.

00:32:07.292 --> 00:32:11.530 align:middle line:84%
