They are there all the time.

00:32:18.137 --> 00:32:19.338 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: OK.

00:32:19.338 --> 00:32:22.341 align:middle line:84%
>> KH: And then, you have
all 188 countries come

00:32:22.341 --> 00:32:24.376 align:middle line:90%
