00:32:28.247 --> 00:32:30.516 align:middle line:84%
And then, in between
those times,

00:32:30.516 --> 00:32:34.386 align:middle line:84%
there is something called the
Development Committee which acts

00:32:34.386 --> 00:32:40.426 align:middle line:84%
to safeguard the interest
of the 188 countries.

00:32:40.426 --> 00:32:41.560 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: OK.

00:32:41.560 --> 00:32:42.995 align:middle line:84%
So they're part of the
Development Committee.

00:32:42.995 --> 00:32:46.432 align:middle line:84%
And now, you just teased us
