00:33:39.485 --> 00:33:41.453 align:middle line:90%
There is room for other--

00:33:41.453 --> 00:33:42.521 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: Other assets.

00:33:42.521 --> 00:33:44.089 align:middle line:84%
>> KH: -- other assets,
other commodities.

00:33:44.089 --> 00:33:45.824 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: Yes.

00:33:45.824 --> 00:33:48.393 align:middle line:84%
>> KH: So, all that has
to happen is we have

00:33:48.393 --> 00:33:52.431 align:middle line:84%
