00:34:01.807 --> 00:34:02.808 align:middle line:90%
>> KH: Yes.

00:34:02.808 --> 00:34:03.976 align:middle line:84%
That's where it makes
a lot of sense.

00:34:03.976 --> 00:34:05.377 align:middle line:84%
>> RM: That makes a lot--
makes perfect sense.

00:34:05.377 --> 00:34:09.814 align:middle line:84%
So if we're looking now at those
markets, now, the same entities,

00:34:09.814 --> 00:34:11.850 align:middle line:84%
at least from what I read
