00:36:00.259 --> 00:36:02.227 align:middle line:84%
that practice has
stopped as of July 7th?

00:36:02.227 --> 00:36:03.428 align:middle line:90%
>> KH: It has stopped it.

00:36:03.428 --> 00:36:06.932 align:middle line:84%
It has stopped because the
people who are leasing,

00:36:06.932 --> 00:36:09.835 align:middle line:84%
