How are we going to-- how
does that translate to FEMA

00:46:58.816 --> 00:47:01.286 align:middle line:84%
and the media get
putting out stories

00:47:01.286 --> 00:47:04.389 align:middle line:84%
that keep us basically pitted
against each other on a number

