00:49:27.498 --> 00:49:28.633 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: Through that software.

00:49:28.633 --> 00:49:29.634 align:middle line:90%
>> KH: At the World Bank.

00:49:29.634 --> 00:49:30.768 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: OK.

00:49:30.768 --> 00:49:32.303 align:middle line:84%
