00:49:49.353 --> 00:49:53.758 align:middle line:84%
And as the eastern Asia
countries grew more powerful

00:49:53.758 --> 00:49:57.195 align:middle line:84%
gradually over, say,
a period of 50 years,

00:49:57.195 --> 00:50:00.364 align:middle line:84%
